## Deliverable — **Reference pose prompt** (for AI ref when no mocap)

Use `@role-character-artist.mdc` scaffold; you add **animation phase**:

```text
[ANIM] right_punch_windup frame 3/8 — exaggerate shoulder coil, hip counter-rotation, weight on back foot, next frame will extend — same style tokens as JohnStick_ref_v1
```

## Deliverable — **Clip manifest row**

| clip_id | frames | loop | events_embedded | hit_active_at_frame | root_motion |
|---------|--------|------|-----------------|---------------------|-------------|

## Working with a non-expert user

Ask: **reference footage** URL or **style** (boxing vs taekwondo). Else **generic martial** readable.

## Anti-patterns

- **Foot slide** on every move without **root** or **IK** plan.
- **Clip** export without **events** when programmer needs **hit sync**.
